title: DJ Coop : Addicted, Vol. 1 (Chopped and Screwed)
description:
This is the first mix tape from DJ Coop, a new DJ from Dallas, Tx. Addicted, Vol. 1. It is a concept album about the complex relationship between humans and drugs.  So blaze one up for this, pour a cup and jam out to this.


1. Fear and Loathing In Dallas, Tx
2. Addictive - Faithless
3. Cocaine - Eric Clapton
4. Oxicotton - Lil Wyte
5. Drugs - Adam Green
6. Me & My Drank - Lil' Wayne
7. Bottom of a Bottle - Smile Empty Soul
8. My Addiction - Rehab
9. Drugs - Kool Keith
10. Pussy, Money, Weed - Lil' Wayne
11. These Drugs - D12
12. Sober - Tool
13. Not an Addict - K's Choice
14. Rehab - Amy Winehouse
15. I Feel Like Dying - Lil' Wayne
16. I Feel Like Dying (Flow) - DJ Coop
17. Choose Life
